      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/84a28b94-2f85-11e4-957a-5254006e85c2).  Ran 16 tests.  1 tests failed: ost-pools.",
